<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<text id="02-output-contract" title="Clean Architecture Output Contract" version="1.1.0" est_tokens="900" depth="essential">
  <summary>JSON Schema (draft-07) for the spec artefact this methodology produces, plus valid + invalid examples and forbidden patterns.</summary>

  <section title="Schema">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
  "type": "object",
  "required": [
    "layers",
    "import_direction_lint",
    "entity_test_max_ms",
    "events_after_persist",
    "one_aggregate_per_tx",
    "mapper_max_lines"
  ],
  "properties": {
    "layers": {
      "type": "array",
      "minItems": 4,
      "items": {
        "enum": [
          "entities",
          "use_cases",
          "interface_adapters",
          "frameworks"
        ]
      }
    },
    "import_direction_lint": {
      "const": true
    },
    "entity_test_max_ms": {
      "type": "integer",
      "maximum": 100
    },
    "events_after_persist": {
      "enum": [
        "commit-then-publish",
        "transactional-outbox"
      ]
    },
    "one_aggregate_per_tx": {
      "const": true
    },
    "mapper_max_lines": {
      "type": "integer",
      "maximum": 10
    }
  }
}
]]></code>
  </section>

  <example valid="true">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "layers": [
    "entities",
    "use_cases",
    "interface_adapters",
    "frameworks"
  ],
  "import_direction_lint": true,
  "entity_test_max_ms": 100,
  "events_after_persist": "transactional-outbox",
  "one_aggregate_per_tx": true,
  "mapper_max_lines": 10
}
]]></code>
  </example>

  <example valid="false">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "layers": [
    "all"
  ],
  "import_direction_lint": false,
  "entity_test_max_ms": 500,
  "events_after_persist": "fire-and-forget",
  "one_aggregate_per_tx": false,
  "mapper_max_lines": 80
}
]]></code>
    <note>layers collapsed (r1); no lint (r1); slow entity tests (r2); fire-and-forget events (r3); multi-aggregate tx (r4); fat mapper (r5).</note>
  </example>

  <output-contract>
    <forbidden>
      <pattern id="f1">import_direction_lint is false (r1)</pattern>
      <pattern id="f2">entity_test_max_ms >100 (r2)</pattern>
      <pattern id="f3">events_after_persist is `fire-and-forget` or missing (r3)</pattern>
      <pattern id="f4">one_aggregate_per_tx is false (r4)</pattern>
      <pattern id="f5">mapper_max_lines >10 (r5)</pattern>
    </forbidden>
  </output-contract>

  <reference path="scripts/validate-clean-architecture.py">Validator script</reference>
</text>
